                    <h2 class="h4 mb-0">What Are Templates?</h2>
                </div>

                <p class="text-muted mb-3">
                    A template is a pre-configured session blueprint — it contains the session title, goal, join form fields,
                    and a full sequenced list of activities with their settings. When you use a template, all of this is imported
                    into a brand-new session with a fresh session code. The original template is never modified.
                </p>

